com.interpss.core.aclf.facts
Interface StaticVarCompensator

All Superinterfaces:
AclfControlBus, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, IAclfAdjustment, NameTag, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
All Known Implementing Classes:
StaticVarCompensatorImpl
public interface StaticVarCompensator
extends AclfControlBus

A representation of the model object 'Switch Cap Bank'. Use the bus Q (of this bus) to control the voltage of a remote bus (could be this bus) or reactive power output of another bus. The remote bus could be this bus itself, can not be a GenPV or Swing bus. RemoteQBus id is the same as the busId of this bus.

The following features are supported:

  • DQ dv
  • Vq Limit
  • BInit
  • Remote Bus
  • QArray
